text: "All Shook Up" is a 1957 song by Elvis Presley and went to number 1 in the United States for 8 weeks and number 1 in the United Kingdom. It went on to be covered by Suzi Quatro and Billy Joel for the 1992 movie Honeymoon in Vegas. Category:1957 songs Category:Elvis Presley songs Category:Billy Joel songs Category:Suzi Quatro songs
title: All Shook Up
